<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <link  rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/user-landing.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nerko+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="nav-bar">
        <div class="nav-logo-container">
            <img src="../../resources/Icon.svg" alt="Website Icon" class="logo-img">
            <h1 class="nav-title">Wallet Watcher</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-buttons">
            
            <button class="nav-button nav-user-btn" id="logoutButton">Log Out</button>
            <button class="theme-changer" id="themeBtn">
                <img src="../../resources/ionicons/sunny.svg" id="changeIcon" data-theme="sunny" alt="☀️" class="change-icon"/>
            </button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="landing-section">
        <h1 class="landing-title">Welcome Back <br><%= locals.name || "User" %></h1>
        
        <div class="cards">
            <div class="card card-1">
    
                <div class="card-title"><h3>Modify Income Streams</h3></div>
                <div class="card-middle-background">
                    <img class="card-img" src="../../resources/banking-icons/piggy-bank.svg" alt="">
                    <button class="view-button view-button-1" id="incomesButton"></button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-bottom card-bottom-1">

                    Here you can view you current income streams. 

                    <br>
                    <br>

                    You can add and view new income streams here that will contribute to your net. Enter incomes that will occur after a certain amount of time; i.e. monthly, weekly, etc...

                
                </div>
            </div>
    
            <div class="card card-2">
    
                <div class="card-title">
                    <h3>Modify Expenses</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-middle-background">
                    <img class="card-img" src="../../resources/banking-icons/money.svg" alt="">
                    <button class="view-button view-button-2" id="expensesButton"></button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-bottom card-bottom-2">
                    Here you can modify your expenses. 

                    <br>
                    <br>

                    You can add and view new and old expenses that contribute to your net. Expenses can be entered in over differnet time intervals like monthly, weekly, etc... 
                </div>
            </div>
    
            <div class="card card-3">
    
                <div class="card-title"><h3>View Account Balance</h3></div>
                <div class="card-middle-background">
                    <img class="card-img" src="../../resources/banking-icons/bank.svg" alt="">
                    <button class="view-button view-button-3" id="balanceButton"></button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-bottom card-bottom-3">
                    Here you can view your balances and net.
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    Create new balances for different things you may need like car, phone, bills,  etc... 
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    View your net income that takes into account all your incomes and expenses. 
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

